Cash recognized the value in cryptocurrency as a secure and deflationary money, but didn‚Äôt fall in love with Bitcoin. fields.Bio:
ReFi Korea introduces the refi movement to Seoul.
ReFi Korea is a community dedicated to promoting financial inclusion and wealth redistribution through the use of blockchain technology. We believe that the decentralized and transparent nature of blockchain has the potential to empower individuals and communities by providing access to fair and efficient financial services. Our mission is to educate and raise awareness about the benefits of blockchain and the Refi movement in Seoul, South Korea. We publish research articles, provide educational resources, and hold regular meetups to bring together like-minded individuals and organizations.

In Korea, there are many projects related to the environment, mainly cute NFT projects. In fact, very few people in Korea know the concept of refi, so we wrote an article to promote refi. And we hosted a session with a former Open Forest Protocol employee.Based on the published article, we are going to onboard Korean web2 people by April. It is because there are few people in the blockchain industry who are engaged in the impact field. And until now, I was only active in Korea, but I'm trying to communicate a lot with overseas.
